remarks: Lemma for ~ frege57b .  Proposition 55 of [Frege1879] p. 50. Note that ~ eqtr2 incorporates ~ eqcom which is stronger than this proposition which is identical to ~ equcomi .  Is is possible that Frege tricked himself into assuming what he was out to prove?  (Contributed by RP, 24-Dec-2019.)  (Proof modification is discouraged.)
